query:
UPDATE events
                SET event_type_id = $1
                    , game_system_id = $2
                    , title = $3
                    , description = $4
                    , start_dt = $5
                    , end_dt = $6
                    , year = $7
                    , cost = $8
                    , tickets_available = $9
                    , min_players = $10
                    , max_players = $11
                    , age_requirement = $12
                    , required_experience = $13
                    , table_number = $14
                    , materials_id = $15
                    , contact_id = $16
                    , website_id = $17
                    , group_id = $18
                WHERE id = $19
